sick-leaves-over-call-or-text/articleshow/132158282.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/wheres-the-doctors-note-germany-tightens-workplace-rules-no-more-sick-leaves-over-call-or-text/articleshow/132158282.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T15:29:44+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI News Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132158310,imgsize-50909.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Texas school was secretly using stolen gas to heat its classrooms, then one invisible leak killed 295 people in seconds]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132157791.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/texas-school-was-secretly-using-stolen-gas-to-heat-its-classrooms-then-one-invisible-leak-killed-295-people-in-seconds/articleshow/132157791.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/texas-school-was-secretly-using-stolen-gas-to-heat-its-classrooms-then-one-invisible-leak-killed-295-people-in-seconds/articleshow/132157791.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T15:26:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132157977,imgsize-1713632.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Government extends pub opening until 5am for England's World Cup match against Mexico]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132157326.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Pubs and bars across England and Wales can now stay open until 5 am on Monday, allowing fans to watch England's World Cup last-16 clash against Mexico until the final whistle. This special licensing extension, granted by the UK government using emergency powers, avoids the need for individual venue applications.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/government-extends-pub-opening-until-5am-for-englands-world-cup-match-against-mexico/articleshow/132157326.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/government-extends-pub-opening-until-5am-for-englands-world-cup-match-against-mexico/articleshow/132157326.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T14:45:05+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132157403,imgsize-92142.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Owens Questions Erika Kirk Grief: criticises widow’s response to death; revisits leaked call]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132146634.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens used her Shawn Ryan Show interview to criticize Erika Kirk’s response to Charlie Kirk’s death. Owens claimed Nick Fuentes appeared more emotional than Charlie’s widow and revisited earlier complaints about Erika’s behavior after the tragedy. The comments add another chapter to the ongoing public feud between Owens and Erika Kirk, which has continued for months.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/candace-owens-ignites-charlie-kirk-death-controversy-says-nick-fuentes-seemed-more-impassioned-than-erika-kirk/articleshow/132146634.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/candace-owens-ignites-charlie-kirk-death-controversy-says-nick-fuentes-seemed-more-impassioned-than-erika-kirk/articleshow/132146634.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T00:40:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132146548,imgsize-597895.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why do goats climb trees in Morocco: The surprising science behind their forest-saving habit]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132157123.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/why-do-goats-climb-trees-in-morocco-the-surprising-science-behind-their-forest-saving-habit/articleshow/132157123.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/why-do-goats-climb-trees-in-morocco-the-surprising-science-behind-their-forest-saving-habit/articleshow/132157123.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T14:44:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132157375,imgsize-1376749.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[102 missed alerts, broken anti-drone system: US govt watchdog details security failures in 2024 Trump shooting]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132153992.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A critical report reveals the US Secret Service missed crucial local police radio chatter about the gunman who targeted President Trump in Pennsylvania. The agency also lacked a joint communications hub, receiving minimal alerts. This failure, coupled with an inoperable counter-drone system that missed a pre-attack drone flight, left the President's security vulnerable. The incident resulted in casualties and injuries.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/102-missed-alerts-broken-anti-drone-system-us-govt-watchdog-details-security-failures-in-2024-trump-shooting/articleshow/132153992.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/102-missed-alerts-broken-anti-drone-system-us-govt-watchdog-details-security-failures-in-2024-trump-shooting/articleshow/132153992.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T14:37:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132157318,imgsize-1193590.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Battling a heatwave? Here's how the right thermostat fan setting can help you feel cooler]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132156688.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Your thermostat's fan setting, often overlooked, significantly impacts home comfort and energy bills. While 'Auto' conserves electricity and improves summer humidity control by running the fan only during heating/cooling cycles, 'On' offers consistent temperatures and better air filtration. For allergy sufferers or those with pets, 'On' might be beneficial despite higher costs. Consider your household's priorities to choose the best setting.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/home-garden/battling-a-heatwave-heres-how-the-right-thermostat-fan-setting-can-help-you-feel-cooler/articleshow/132156688.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/home-garden/battling-a-heatwave-heres-how-the-right-thermostat-fan-setting-can-help-you-feel-cooler/articleshow/132156688.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T14:32:17+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Lifestyle Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132156727,imgsize-113101.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[A giant 3,200-year-old city hidden beneath Ireland may rewrite Europe's ancient history]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-