ans-donated-227-tonnes-of-gold-to-rescue-their-economy-after-the-1997-imf-bailout/articleshow/132152270.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/how-south-koreans-donated-227-tonnes-of-gold-to-rescue-their-economy-after-the-1997-imf-bailout/articleshow/132152270.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T10:06:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132152495,imgsize-1308897.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Is July 3 a federal holiday? What is open and closed on Friday ahead of Fourth of July]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132153502.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[As the United States gears up for its 250th birthday on Saturday, July 4, 2026, the preceding Friday, July 3, will be observed as a federal holiday. While most retail stores and postal services will operate normally, banks will be open with potential adjusted hours. The stock market, however, will be closed. State DMVs and city offices will see varied closures, so checking local schedules is advised.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/is-july-3-a-federal-holiday-what-is-open-and-closed-on-friday-ahead-of-fourth-of-july/articleshow/132153502.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/is-july-3-a-federal-holiday-what-is-open-and-closed-on-friday-ahead-of-fourth-of-july/articleshow/132153502.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T11:47:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI News Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132153586,imgsize-178033.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ford fired an 11-year employee over a $1.95 cookie, then his bank statement changed everything]]></title><descri